ef subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00710">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 22. 7. 1897</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
